@Andy W.
@all

I remember when it used to be a joke that someone bought a "Mickey Mouse" watch.  There really were toy Mickey Mouse watches (I presume Disney made some money off them), but they didn't really work.

So for a long time it was a joke that someone bought a cheap "Mickey Mouse" watch.

Then later, some genius make a few buck producing actual working (for the most part) watches with MM's face.

